# DSSData

[![PyPI version](https://badge.fury.io/py/dssdata.svg)](https://pypi.org/project/dssdata/)
[![DOI](https://zenodo.org/badge/250637349.svg)](https://zenodo.org/badge/latestdoi/250637349)
